<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西低头看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>紫色的粘液把她的脚紧紧粘在了地面上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呀啊！”罗西用她的超能力用力地扯，用力地扭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于——哧！——她的双脚自由了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是外星人已经打开了比萨外卖车的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”司机叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快停下！”罗西冲着外星人们飞去并喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会让你们伤害他的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不会伤害任何人。”一个外星人说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫布里姆。我们需要给飞船补充燃料。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>飞船用食物作燃料，但是这些食物都没用。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么没用？”罗西问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些食物种类都不对。”布里姆说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要又厚又黏的食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又厚又黏？”罗西问道，“嗯……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”玛拉说，“我把牛肉酱沾到袖子上面了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真糟糕。”杰克说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>紧接着布里姆和别的外星人一起走进了食堂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“外星人！”有人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快跑啊！”有人叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火箭女孩儿飞了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要惊慌。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些外星人很友好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们只是需要一些牛肉酱来作燃料启动飞船。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在火箭女孩儿解释了一切之后，大家不再害怕了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢！你可以拿走我的牛肉酱！”杰克说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把我的也拿走吧！”玛拉说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有我的！”特勒尔说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请大家拿着午餐跟我们来。”火箭女孩儿说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在来试一下，布里姆。”罗西说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布里姆尝试着启动飞船，飞船完美启动了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢大家。”布里姆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些牛肉酱真是我们飞船的完美燃料。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们向飞走的飞船挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很开心我们摆脱了那些牛肉酱。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我们现在要吃什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看窗外！”玛拉说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“比萨！”杰克叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长走进了食堂，他手里面端着一大摞比萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们为了拯救美罗城而放弃了午餐。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我请大家吃比萨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>学生们都欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，罗西走进了食堂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西！”玛拉喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你错过了火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有外星人！”杰克叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”罗西说道，装作一副很惊讶的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你去哪儿了？”马拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我在帮助潘校长做一些……办公室的工作。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔怀疑地看了看罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道吗，罗西？你错了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火箭女孩儿真的把我们从牛肉酱面包里解救了出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西什么也没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她只是笑了笑，静静地拿起了一块比萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>